Katherine Victor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Katherine_Victor 0 Katherine Victor (born Katena Ktenavea, August 18, 1923 – October 22, 2004), was an American actress, perhaps best known for her roles in Ron Ormond's Mesa of Lost Women (1953) and Jerry Warren films. She was also known as Katina Vea.
